title: #92Noon Marney Gellner in for PA! Meatsauce/Leber/Kleinsasser/Zimmer Presser/Petersen/Saric/Taft
description: Marney Gellner from FOX Sports North fills in for PA and welcomes some great guests into the Bryant Heating & Cooling Studios! Meatsauce starts the show with Marney before former Vikings Jim Kleinsasser and Ben Leber talk all things football and life after football. Mike Zimmer holds his presser. Timberwolves TV analyst Jim Petersen talks Wolves basketball before Dario Šarić calls in to talk about his team's recent success. Plus, Edina native and FS1 host Jenny Taft calls in to talk about her life in LA!
